        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><h1 id="C-编程练习题集"><a href="#C-编程练习题集" class="headerlink" title="C++ 编程练习题集"></a>C++ 编程练习题集</h1><h2 id="7-1-Programming-in-C-is-fun"><a href="#7-1-Programming-in-C-is-fun" class="headerlink" title="7-1 Programming in C is fun!"></a>7-1 Programming in C is fun!</h2><p><strong>题目描述：</strong><br>本题要求编写程序，输出一个短句“Programming in C is fun!”。</p><p><strong>输入格式：</strong><br>本题目没有输入。</p><p><strong>输出格式：</strong><br>在一行中输出短句“Programming in C is fun!”。</p><p><strong>参考代码：</strong></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Programming in C is fun!&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="7-2-输出带框文字"><a href="#7-2-输出带框文字" class="headerlink" title="7-2 输出带框文字"></a>7-2 输出带框文字</h2><p><strong>题目描述：</strong><br>本题要求编写程序，输出指定的带框文字。</p><p><strong>输入格式：</strong><br>本题无输入。</p><p><strong>输出格式：</strong><br>按照下列格式输出带框文字。</p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">************</span><br><span class="line">  Welcome</span><br><span class="line">************</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>参考代码：</strong></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;************\n  Welcome\n************&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="7-3-输出三角形"><a href="#7-3-输出三角形" class="headerlink" title="7-3 输出三角形"></a>7-3 输出三角形</h2><p><strong>题目描述：</strong><br>本题要求编写程序，输出指定的由“*”组成的三角图案。</p><p><strong>输入格式：</strong><br>本题无输入。</p><p><strong>输出格式：</strong><br>按照下列格式输出由“*”组成的三角图案。</p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">****</span><br><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">**</span><br><span class="line">*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>参考代码：</strong></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;****\n***\n**\n*&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="7-4-和-C-打招呼"><a href="#7-4-和-C-打招呼" class="headerlink" title="7-4 和 C++ 打招呼"></a>7-4 和 C++ 打招呼</h2><p><strong>题目描述：</strong><br>入门的第一个 C++ 程序。从键盘输入学生姓名，然后输出指定格式的内容。</p><p><strong>输入格式：</strong><br>学生姓名。</p><p><strong>输出格式：</strong></p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hello, C++!</span><br><span class="line">My name is &lt;学生姓名&gt;.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>输入样例：</strong></p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">张三</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>输出样例：</strong></p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hello, C++!</span><br><span class="line">My name is 张三.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>新手提示：</strong></p><ol><li>姓名需要从键盘读入，不是固定的值；</li><li>注意检查输出内容的每一个符号，包括大小写，空格，标点，都要与输出格式完全一致。</li></ol><p><strong>参考代码：</strong></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    string name;</span><br><span class="line">    cin &gt;&gt; name;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Hello, C++!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;My name is &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; name &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;.&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="7-5-两数之和"><a href="#7-5-两数之和" class="headerlink" title="7-5 两数之和"></a>7-5 两数之和</h2><p><strong>题目描述：</strong><br>求两个整数之和。</p><p><strong>输入格式：</strong><br>在一行中输入两个整数 A 和 B，两个整数之间用空格隔开。</p><p><strong>输出格式：</strong><br>输出 A+B 的值。</p><p><strong>输入样例：</strong></p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">18 -299</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>输出样例：</strong></p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-281</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>参考代码：</strong></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> a, b;</span><br><span class="line">    cin &gt;&gt; a &gt;&gt; b;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; a + b;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
